            </ul>
            <div class="votes">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <span>5.7(76)</span>
                <p><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 2326 views</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="receipt-main">
            <div class="receipt-main-image">
                <img src="/images/Salads/meat-salad.jpg" alt="meat-salad">
            </div>
            <div class="receipt-main-products">
                <h4>Products:</h4>
                <ol type="1">
                    <li>2 grated cucumbers </li>
                    <li>3 carrots, chopped</li>
                    <li>150 - 200 g duck meat</li>
                    <li>2 green peppers</li>
                    <li> 150 - 200 g chicken</li>
                    <li>1 tablespoon vinegar</li>
                    <li>2 tablespoon oil</li>
                    <li>1 cup of salt</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="receipt-content">
            <h4>Receipt:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Wash the vegetables and grate them on a larger grater.</li>
                <li>Cut the meat into thin strips and smell it for about 30 minutes in a saucepan. Once it has cooled, salt it and marinate with vinegar.</li>
                <li>Put all the products in a wide plate and pour with the oil.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </article>
    <article>
        <h2>Shopska salata</h2>
        <div class="receipt-header">
            <ul>
                <li><h4>Preparation</h4> <i class="far fa-clock"></i> <span>16 min</span></li>
                <li><h4>Cooking</h4> <i class="fas fa-cookie-bite"></i> <span>34 min</span></li>
                <li><h4>Portions</h4> <i class="fas fa-coffee"></i> <span>16-19</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="votes">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
